ComicInfo.Summary:
*SERIES FINALE! HUGE, TRIPLE-SIZED ISSUE!* OH, THE PLACES... The grand finale of Zenescope's longest running title is here in this over-sized event issue! Sela, the students of Arcane Acre, and the Realm Knights, enter the final battle against Bloody Bones! Wonderland, Neverland, Oz, Myst and Earth must stand together against the greatest threat to ever threaten the realms of power.
